1) Programmes to show Pi is working
  upload PiHere.py and SubAlertPi.py to all Pis
  run both programmes
  the Pi-here sends a MQTT message
  the subscription programme monitors message receipt and sends an email if it stops


2) RSSI strength
  copy rssi.py, rssi_log.txt and upload_rssi_log.py to same directory
  run rssi.py and the upload programme
  have the sensors active and near by
  Open Blynk device

3) Angular movement and Blynk heartbeat
  copy test.py and device_model.py to same directory
  run test.py

